snippet.title: TF2 Classic - TF2Maps Developer Interview & Beta Preview
snippet.description:
Suna interviews TF2 Classic lead developers Waugh101 and sniffy194 as a part of the annual TF2Maps Jam livestream, while showcasing an early preview of the in-development Patch 2.2.0.

00:11 - vip_badwater
